Welcome to Ikariam Clone using CodeIgnighter

First things first you will Need:
a web server capable of hosting php/mysql
ability to use mod rewirte on server
and basic script knowledge.

To set this game up its as easy as uploading the script to host

the .htaccess is set up to allow subdomains incase you want more worlds
it also needs to be edited  to fit your own server

The following files also need to be configured
application/config/config.php
application/config/autoloader.php
application/config/ikariam.php
application/config/database.php

Currently we are working on adding missing files to clone,
Then translating 100% so then we can add more languages to game

Keep eyes out on RAGEZONE FORUMS for more details

Advocaite.

